'''''Omo Ghetto''''' (English translation: '''''Child of the Ghetto)''''' ni filimi yasohotse 2010 muri [[Nigeria]]  iyoborwa na Abiodun Olarenwaju, Star Funke Akindele, Rasheli Oniga, Taiwo Hassan, Yinka Quadri na Eniola Badmus <ref>Omo Ghetto: The Saga' Becomes Highest-Grossing ... <nowiki>https://www.premiumtimesng.com</nowiki> › entertainment › 43...</ref>.<ref>Movie Review: 'Omo Ghetto: The Saga' is an engaging tribute ... (premiumtimesng.com)</ref> 

== Umugambi ==
Filime ishingiye ku ngeso mbi za societe nitsinda ryiganjemo abagore.<ref>'Omo Ghetto: The Saga' is coming to Netflix! | Pulse Nigeria <nowiki>https://www.pulse.ng</nowiki> › Entertainment › Movies</ref>

== Kwakira ==
Olusegun Michael wo muri ''[[Gana]] ya none'' yashimye uwo mugambi, gukina, insanganyamatsiko no gusobanura uruhare muri iyi filime, avuga ko ari filime "idakora, ishimishije kandi ihishura"<ref>"Omo Ghetto (The Saga)" Is Coming To Netflix On Sept. 10 <nowiki>https://guardian.ng</nowiki> › life › film › omo-ghetto-the-saga-i...</ref>.  Muri 2017, Azeezat Kareem wo mu kinyamakuru Encomium Magazine yashyize ahagaragara ''Omo Ghetto'' nka imwe muri filime ebyiri zatumye Eniola Badmus amenyekana cyane mu nganda za firime zo muri [[Nijeriya]]<ref>'Omo Ghetto: The Saga' wins international award - PM News ... <nowiki>https://pmnewsnigeria.com</nowiki> › Entertainment › Nollywood</ref>.  Yashyizwe kandi muri Legit.ng film eshanu "zitazibagirana" za Funke Akindele <ref>'Omo Ghetto (The Saga)' is now the highest-grossing ... <nowiki>https://africa.businessinsider.com</nowiki> › Local › Lifestyle</ref>. 

